{"tid":1072248,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙中綫紅磡站覆檢 四鋼筋不合格","createTime":"2019-03-22T01:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T02:32:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"329c3549f94ecf1a29807148435abb6ca9980c2d","tid":1072248,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190322/20638828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F20638828&d=nGD0VYfdVRVKlmm%2FccroE%2FcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=750dc6c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190322%2F20638828&h=d8acf748\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190322/20638828</a><br />\n<br />\n沙中綫紅磡站覆檢 四鋼筋不合格<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190322/large/22la9p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190322%2Flarge%2F22la9p2.jpg&h=8f83cd12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙中綫紅磡站鋼筋的不合格比率約32%。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵上周在沙中綫紅磡站月台層板，恢復用超音波檢測法量度鋼筋扭入螺絲帽的長度。路政署昨公佈17支鋼筋接駁樣本的覆檢結果，其中有4支不合格。另外，今次覆檢有7支鋼筋樣本由不合格變合格，有2支則由合格變不合格。<br />\n<br />\n路政署昨公佈的17支樣本檢測結果，螺絲帽位置主要分佈在東西走廊C1、C2和C3區的月台層板近西面連續牆底部。有13支鋼筋扭入螺絲帽的長度達37毫米或以上，視為合格。大部份樣本均外露1至2個扭紋，有兩個樣本則外露2至3個扭紋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190322/large/a1002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190322%2Flarge%2Fa1002a.gif&h=b5bc0030&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七支樣本「肥佬」變合格<br />\n<br />\n有4支鋼筋扭入螺絲帽的長度則少於37毫米被列為不合格，長度介乎34.8毫米至36.8毫米，分佈在東西走廊C1和C2區。連同路政署星期一公佈的首輪覆檢結果，現時不合格比率約32%。<br />\n<br />\n今次公佈的樣本全為重新再驗。比較政府過往檢測結果，今次結果當中有7支樣本由不合格變成合格，誤差最大是其中一支在東西走廊C2區月台層板近西面連續牆底部的樣本，之前稱只扭入32.97毫米，重新檢測後增至39.3毫米，相差6.33毫米。<br />\n<br />\n另有2支鋼筋重檢後由合格變成不合格，其中一支的扭入結果由37.77毫米下調至34.8毫米，相差2.97毫米。<br />\n<br />\n■記者羅繼盛  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n泛民促港府取回審批權 削單程證議案否決<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n西環集中營：明日大嶼要兩代港人埋單 (季陶)"},{"pid":"f3fa576dbc6e3eb5bd3b529d69b212fc7a670072","tid":1072248,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"Ok la<br />\n驗到合格為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd9614ab8168bf115557adb7de4d80b874d47813","tid":1072248,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:00:26.000Z","msg":"唔好驗啦<br />\n由佢通車啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"326c2079d492bdff3cb501ae2e57c190f4836c93","tid":1072248,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:30:11.000Z","msg":"死人都無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港豬咁平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab64df195e5443a057e13eb3c0a9e96edcab4c32","tid":1072248,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"一句講曬 <br />\n下一步諗住點？ 重建定通車"}]}